data: "The Popcorn Thief/The Little Tornado/She Flies Through the Air"

The Popcorn Thief - Tubby is hired for detective work at Annie's home cinema, enduring a girly night. It turns out he's in league with the popcorn snatchers Iggy and Willy. The Little Tornado - Believing Lulu has super strength, Tubby permits her into his club. When they assign her to take care of the West Side Gang, a small tornado takes care of them. She Flies Through the Air - Lulu and Tubby go skiing at Hilltop Mountain. Accidental mishaps going downhill make Lulu an honorary ski champion.

data: In an attempt to reform Eddie Lipsky (a.k.a. "Motor Ed"), his aunt places him under the care of his cousin, Dr. Drakken. Together the two plot to steal the technology powering Felix's chair while he and Ron are at a video game convention. In the meantime Kim is jealous of all the time Ron is spending with Felix so she "TJI's" (tries joining in), even though what they enjoy doing is not her thing.

In an attempt to foil yet another scheme of Drakken to steal from Cyrus Bortel, experimental mood altering devices accidentally get attached to Kim and Shego. During the chaos, Ron accidentally picks up the control for the devices instead of the Kimmunicator, activating them. As a result confusion for both Ron and Drakken ensues as the former mistakes the device for a video game as it sends the girls hurtling through a range of emotions, including anger, sorrow, and even love- which means major mayhem for Ron and Drakken.

When Ron wants to avoid his devilishly warped Cousin Shawn at a wedding Kim subtly suggests than Ron take her as a friendly date. Ron finds this 'awkweird' and backs down. Drakken meanwhile attempts to use a HenchCo device called the Attitudinator to make himself even more evil. The plan fails when Kim and Ron break the machine gradually turning Ron into an eccentric super villain and Drakken into a goody-baking sweetie.

Note: This is the first time Kim and Ron meet Wade in person.

table-0707-397.caption: Fundamental design and Range Description
data: Abu Dhabi license plates can either have Red, Blue, Green or Grey bands on left or middle sides, or feature one of the numbers 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12 or 13 in red bands on top or left side. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Ajman license plates can have one of the letters: A, B or C. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Dubai license plates can either have one of the letters: A to Z, or be a white plate. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Fujairah license plates can either have one of the letters: A to G, K, M, P, R, S, or T, or be a white plate. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Ras al-Khaimah license plates can either have one of the letters: A, C, D, I, K, M, N, S, V or Y, be a white plate, or feature a fort on the top side of the plate. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Sharjah license plates can either contain one of the numbers: 1 or 2, or either be an orange or a white plate. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
Umm al-Quwain license plates can either have one of the letters: A, B, G or X, or be a white plate. Numbers contain maximum 5 digits.
